0x5F3A3574.name: SET_VEHICLE_AUTO_REPAIR_DISABLED

params.name: vehicle
params.description: The vehicle to set disable auto vehicle repair.

params.name: value
params.description: Setting the value to  true prevents the vehicle from being repaired when a extra is enabled. Setting the value to false allows the vehicle from being repaired when a extra is enabled.

0x5F3A3574.description: Disables the vehicle from being repaired when a vehicle extra is enabled.
